org.jasig.cas.services

Class AbstractRegisteredServiceAttributeReleasePolicy

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jasig.cas.services.AbstractRegisteredServiceAttributeReleasePolicy
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, RegisteredServiceAttributeReleasePolicy
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ReturnAllAttributeReleasePolicy, ReturnAllowedAttributeReleasePolicy, ReturnMappedAttributeReleasePolicy

    public abstract class AbstractRegisteredServiceAttributeReleasePolicy
extends java.lang.Object
implements RegisteredServiceAttributeReleasePolicy
    Abstract release policy for attributes, provides common shared settings such as loggers and attribute filter config. Subclasses are to provide the behavior for attribute retrieval.
    Since:
    4.1.0
